  <li>ğŸ§¼ Sanitize all user inputs using libraries</li>
  <li>ğŸ›¡ï¸ Add CSRF protection for forms</li>
  <li>ğŸ” Use HTTPS for secure data transport</li>
  <li>ğŸ“Š Add logging and monitoring for suspicious activity</li>
</ul>
